commit.message:
Add go.mod file. (#6)

Add a minimal go.mod file in order to create a v1.0.0 module release.

Simplify range over runes.

There's no behavior change. This is equivalent code, but simpler and
more efficient.
Travis: Use latest stable Go (1.8.1 at this time).

Add license name, use consistent wrapping.

Based on template at https://choosealicense.com/licenses/mit/.
Update Travis to Go 1.7, fix vet issue.

Pollute repository with an extraneous non-executable file.

Resolves #3.

Make library's permissive license more visible.

Closes #1.
Fix test to import moved package.
Add import comment, README, Travis, elaborate on motivation.

sanitized_anchor_name: Squash non-alphanumeric characters into a single dash.

Add tests.
Closes #11.

github_flavored_markdown: Move createSanitizedAnchorName into separate package.

This allows others to import that functionality without all the other
heavier dependencies of this package.
Remove HeaderLink because sanitized_anchor_name.Create should be used
instead.
